{"tid":1220781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家記住星期日遊行除左反送中 仲有個好重要既訴求！！！","createTime":"2019-06-14T05:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T17:36:34.000Z","uid":28068,"like":305,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"f48c50b8adb79793fd6a637ee57b3b9b1cc59444","tid":1220781,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:25:35.000Z","msg":"就係釋放並取消控告所有因為呢幾日抗爭而被捕既人！！！<br />\n唔可以再眼白白睇住佢地因抗爭而入獄！！！"},{"pid":"2838dbe934d979a730a7f7e9cf209abc967c6f5a","tid":1220781,"uid":28068,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:28:04.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"41748c8d632fe411313fdaf656590f7cd669e43d","tid":1220781,"uid":28068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:28:18.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d539f1023ba7fc0b4cc1b81801705c354c015279","tid":1220781,"uid":233327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:28:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57708f58177f817b4291cf02f4655047e7ed1a33","tid":1220781,"uid":185476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:28:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63153b3b9400dba3ee40bf828363b96965abcd05","tid":1220781,"uid":28068,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:29:12.000Z","msg":"發現主流post都忘記左要爭取釋放並取消任何控告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418881ab5aaebd66e2863ba4b57e3991aabbb2e9","tid":1220781,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd74dec7c0869be1c87c204c0a5fa3c06017d7d","tid":1220781,"uid":63311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:29:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一日淋病唔撤回 一日都未成功！！！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"adea7a0b5cc75bfc91c1df3c364f895a5e15a53b"